諷誦説(fěng sòng shuō)　“recites, chants and preaches”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://諷誦讀">諷誦讀</a>(fěng sòng dú); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at HD.  11.348.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 441b13.若<span style="color: #8B0000">諷</span><span style="color: #8B0000">誦</span>(Sh.+讀)<span style="color: #8B0000">説</span>深般若波羅蜜時，其心疑於法者，亦不肯學，……… (p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 91.8 = R. 181.10 = AAA. 398.6..<i>bhāṣyāmāṇa~ deśyamāna~ upadiśyamāna~ uddiśyamāna~</i> (“[when the perfection of wisdom is] being taught, demonstrated, expounded and explained”); ZQ. 488a11.學誦; Zfn. 523a9.諷誦讀; Kj. 550c28.説; Xz(I). 801a14.説; Xz(II). 884c8.説; Sh. 615b13.説; Tib.Pk. 110a1 = D. 102b2..<i>’chad pa dang ston pa dang nye bar ston pa</i>; </p>


