荒澤(huāng zé)　“a wilderness, wild countryside”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at HD.  9.393.; DK. 9.659c(呉子, 漢紀); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 455b23.譬若有人行大<span style="color: #8B0000">荒</span><span style="color: #8B0000">澤</span>中，畏盜賊，心念言：“我當何時脱出是阨道中去？”　當棄遠是婬泆，畏懼如行大荒澤中。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 166.4 = R. 332.20 = AAA. 682.4..-kāntāra- (“a large wood, forest, wilderness” [MW , s.v.]); ZQ. 495b17.大空澤; Zfn. 527c28.大空澤; Kj. 565a17.險道; Xz(I). 827c6.險路; Xz(II). 902a12.險路; Sh. 642c19.險難; Tib.Pk. 198a1 = D. 184a3..dgon pa; </p>


