彌勒
彌勒(mí lè;)(mjiei[mjiei:] lǝk)>(QYS. mjie4[mjie:4] lǝk)　　(a transliteration of a certain Middle Indic form (e.g. *<i>Metreka</i>;  cf. Tocharian <i>Maitrāk</i>, <i>Metrak</i>, Bactrian <i>Mētraga</i>;  cf. Ji Xianlin 1998 : 62f., Karashima 2006: 356 = 2007: 294) which corresponds to BHS. <i>Maitreya</i> (name of a bodhisattva))　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 425c6.佛在羅閲祇耆闍崛山中。摩訶比丘僧不可計──諸弟子舍利弗、須菩提等；摩訶 {薩}菩薩無央數──<span style="color: #8B0000">彌</span><span style="color: #8B0000">勒</span>菩薩、文殊師利菩薩等。月十五日説戒時。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at AS. 1.5f.= R. 3.13f.=  AAA. 8.17f.; ps-ZQ. 478b-5.-; not found at  Zfn. 508b.-9f.; not found at  Kj. 537a.-5f.; Xz(I). 763b6f.-; Xz(II). 865c8.慈氏; not found at  Sh. 587a7f.; not found at Tib.Pk. 1b5f.=  D. 1b3f.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 438a-16; (not found at AS. 69.2 = R. 135.3 =  AAA. 325.4..<i>Maitreya</i>; ZQ. 486a20.慈氏; Zfn. 519c-9.彌勒; Kj. 547c13.彌勒; Xz[I]. 790c.-10.慈氏; Xz[II]. 880b23..慈氏; Sh. 608a-17.慈氏; Tib.Pk. 81a3 = D. 76a1..<i>Byams pa</i>)</p>

