菩薩行(pú sà xíng)　“course of conduct of a bodhisattva”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at HD.  9.449.; Krsh(1998). 314, Krsh(2001). 198; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 476b9.佛音聲亦如是。其法皆從因縁起。亦不可從<span style="color: #8B0000">菩</span><span style="color: #8B0000">薩</span><span style="color: #8B0000">行</span>得，亦不可離<span style="color: #8B0000">菩</span><span style="color: #8B0000">薩</span><span style="color: #8B0000">行</span>得；亦不可從佛身得，亦不可離佛身得。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at AS. 254.31 = R. 516.5 =  AAA. 969.8.; ZQ. 507a16.(不從)闓士行(得，不離)行(得); not found at  Zfn. ; not found at  Kj. 584c12.; not found at  Xz(I). ; not found at  Xz(II). ; not found at  Sh. 674b16.; not found at Tib.Pk. 304a6 =  D. 278b6.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 476c11.菩薩有本行布施，有持戒不犯十事，常隨善師，常等心念十方人，無有能壞者，世世見佛，聞<span style="color: #8B0000">菩</span><span style="color: #8B0000">薩</span><span style="color: #8B0000">行</span>事，堅持不忘，世世不諛諂，常行至誠。賢者！欲知：成佛身如是。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at  AS. ; ZQ. 507b10.闓士聞行(!); not found at  Zfn. ; not found at  Kj. ; not found at  Xz(I). ; not found at  Xz(II). ; not found at  Sh. ; not found at  Tib. ; </p>


