書寫
書寫(shū xiě)　“copies, writes”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://作字">作字</a>(zuò zì); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD. 5.726b(後漢書 etc.); DK. 5.971a(後漢書, 顏氏家訓); Krsh(1998). 418, Krsh(2001). 249, Hu 2002 : 31(道行般若經); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 435b27. 正使不學不持不誦，善男子、善女人但<span style="color: #8B0000">書</span><span style="color: #8B0000">寫</span>，持經卷，自歸作禮，承事，供養名華、搗香、澤香、雜香、繒綵、華蓋旗幡。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 47.4f. = R. 93.11 = AAA. 265.1. .pustakagatām api kṛtvā (“having written down in a book”); not found at  ZQ. 485b6.; Zfn. 517b14.書寫; Kj. 545a20.書寫; Xz(I). 781b19.書; not found at  Xz(II). 877b29.; not found at  Sh. 601c9.; Tib.Pk. 56a2 = D. 53a2. .<i>glegs bam du chud par byas te</i>; </p>

