餘殃
餘殃(yú yāng)　“lingering misfortune (as a result of one’s own misdeeds in previous lives)”#　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD. 12.550a(*[易經 etc.]); DK. 12.405c(*[易經 etc.]); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 459c22. 是輩之人所作宿命悉自見。宿命所作惡於是悉除賜。從是以來斷經<span style="color: #8B0000">餘</span><span style="color: #8B0000">殃</span>悉盡──是宿命惡悉消。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 189.25 = R. 383.10 = AAA. 767.10. .<i>sāvaśeṣa~ karman~</i> (“karma left over [from his refusal of dharma in the past].” [AsP.tr.II  229 = AsP.tr.  150]); ZQ. 498b17 = Lk ; Zfn. 533a9.殃; Kj. 570a13.餘殃; Xz(I). 836c13.餘殃; Xz(II). 908c27.餘殃; Sh. 651b27.餘殃; Tib.Pk. 225b1 = D. 209b4. .<i>lhag ma dang bcas pa’i las</i>; </p>

與
