中直
中直(zhòng zhí)　“fits exactly”(?) or 　“is righteous, right”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD. 1.592b(易經); DK. 1.308a(易經); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 461c3. 須菩提！菩薩當作是知：如擔死人種；無所復<span style="color: #8B0000">中</span><span style="color: #8B0000">直</span>，反呼是菩薩有短；是爲菩薩怨家；是爲厭菩薩。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at AS. 195.27 = R. 394.15 =  AAA. 782.28.; ZQ. 499a26.無所中直; Zfn. 534c4.無所復中; not found at  Kj. 571b4.; not found at  Xz(I). 839a27.; not found at  Xz(II). 910a8.; not found at  Sh. 653c4.; not found at Tib.Pk. 232a3 =  D. 215b4.; </p>

